creator: Julia Caroline Dorr
description:
LibriVox recording of Earlier Poems by Julia Caroline Dorr.
Read in English by Greg Giordano; Olivereading; Andrei Borissenko; Julia Niedermaier; Carol; Lucretia B.; bean420; Ken Masters; Bryony Ford
This is a collection of the earlier poems of Julia Caroline Dorr. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
